description:
While the call is being made to get out of the city, many are being conditioned to stay. The conveniences of city living and the benefits to stay are getting more attractive to those who are spiritually sleeping. It's time to get out before we are told that we have to shelter in place and we are given everything we need to stay under house arrest again. Join us in this episode of Seedtime and Harvest as we make our transition from our summer garden to the fall season.
